<br>
<b>Spirit of Eagle</b><br>
Increase Movement between 57% (L54) to 60% (L60). Outdoor.<br>
<br>
<b>Spirit of Cheetah</b><br>
Increase movement rate by 99-115%. Cancelled when attacked or attacking. Very short duration. Very long recast/memorization time.<br>
<br>
<b>Improved Natural Run Speed</b><br>
Each piont gives around a 10% boost. A player with 3 points runs just slightly slower than a person using Journeyman boots. Indoor/Outdoor.<br>
<br>
<b>Journeyman boots</b><br>
Increase Movement by 35%. Indoor/Outdoor.<br>
<br>
